title: Team Reticent LF D3+ Jg for OOL

embed.description: The latest Tweets from Team Reticent (@TeamReticent). Australian Professional Gaming Organization, featuring teams in DotA 2, CS:GO, SMITE, Rocket League, League of Legends, Call of Duty, Vainglory and Hearthstone!. Australia / International

body: Rank 5 OOL team LF a jungler to play with us for this competitive split. This team is run with a competitive mentality with the goal of making OCS. Having availability in the evenings is a must as we scrim regularly. Add me in-game to discuss.
